    "name": "RNA-seq Variant Discovery",
    "readme": "This workflow performs read alignment with STAR followed by GATK-based variant calling (HaplotypeCaller). It includes pre-processing steps: MarkDuplicates, SplitNCigarReads, and Base Quality Score Recalibration (BQSR).",
